<i>adverb</i>: 한풀 [한풀], 완연히 [와ː년히] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>adverb</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>한풀 [한풀]</dt><br>
<dd>evidently</dd><br>
<dd>기운, 끈기, 의지 등이 눈에 띄게 줄어드는 것을 나타내는 말.</dd><br>
<dd>A word used to indicate that energy, tenacity, will power, etc., weakens noticeably.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>완연히 [와ː년히]</dt><br>
<dd>obviously; evidently</dd><br>
<dd>눈에 보이는 것처럼 아주 뚜렷하게.</dd><br>
<dd>In a very clear manner as if one could see something right before one's eyes.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>